spec_data.Name: perl-Devel-Timer
spec_data.Description:
Devel::Timer allows developers to accurately time how long a specific
piece of code takes to execute. This can be helpful in locating the
slowest parts of an existing application.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:03:53 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Track and report execution time for parts of code
